Package: intervalpsych
Title: Analyzing Interval Data in Psychometrics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Maintainer: Matthias Kloft <kloft.intervalpsych@gmail.com>
Authors@R:
    c(person("Matthias", "Kloft",
